<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Gabriel in der Aren zu Mechelen</head><p>Der Rat bittet um gütliche Anhörung der Nürnberger Bürger wegen des Zolls.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_112" id="55v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_112_r1l1">Dem Erſamen vnd weiſen 
<del rend="strikethrough">Gabrieln Jn </del> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> freund </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_112_r1l2">
<del rend="strikethrough">dem Aren cʒu Me </del> Gabrieln Jn dem Aren cʒu Mechell </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_112_r1l3"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> vvıllig freuntlıch
                        dinſte beuoꝛ Lıeber her Gabriel / Als ~ etliche
                            <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_112_r1l4">
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd kauffleute
                            <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> an euch bringen werden von <del rend="strikethrough">des </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_112_line_1571206175834_165">des </ab></add> cʒolls </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_112_r1l5">wegen cʒu löſen etc / <expan>Bitte<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleiſſikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr Jn darẏnne </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_112_r1l6">durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen geraten
                        vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günſtige hilff vnd fürdrung </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_112_r1l7">bevveiſen wöllet / Als etc das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_112" id="55v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem ersamen und weisen, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>besund<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> freund Gabrieln in dem aren czu Mechell</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan> willig, freuntlich dinste bevor. Lieber her
                        Gabriel, als etliche <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und kauffleute
                            <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> an euch bringen werden von
                            <add>des</add> czolls wegen czu lösen etc.
                            <expan>Bitte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleissikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>, daz ir in darynne durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen geraten und
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günstige hilff und fürdrung beweisen
                        wöllet, als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
